-------------------------------
How to use this thesis?
-------------------------------

Use of PDFLATEX

a) Compiling the document:
  pdflatex main.tex

b) Changing the output name (creates a file called LASTNAME_YEAR.pdf)
  pdflatex --jobname=LASTNAME_YEAR main.tex

c) An optimal workflow is (this should set all pages and references
   correctly):
  pdflatex --jobname=LASTNAME_YEAR main.tex
  bibtex JOBNAME.aux
  pdflatex --jobname=LASTNAME_YEAR main.tex
  pdflatex --jobname=LASTNAME_YEAR main.tex

-------------------------------

Use of BIBTEX

a) To create a file containing your bibliography
  bibtex JOBNAME.aux
